    <title>Scheduling Agreement: Confirmed quantity is higher than Open quantity</title>
    <updated>2024-10-22T14:31:30.620000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>AnkeWerner</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1520176</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hello,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;We have an &lt;SPAN&gt;Scheduling Agreement with Delivery Schedules functionality and I am not able to understand certain behavior of the system.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Cml. dlv. quantity: 52.626&lt;BR /&gt;Cml. released qty: 52.904&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Schedule line with:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Order quantity: 500&lt;BR /&gt;Open quantity: 278 --&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;SPAN&gt;The system calculated the open quantity from the cumulative delivered and cumulative received quantities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;BR /&gt;Confirmed quantity: 500&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="AnkeWerner_0-1729598622220.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/182364iF66F305E0C5A46C4/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="AnkeWerner_0-1729598622220.png" alt="AnkeWerner_0-1729598622220.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Why the system confimed 500 instead of just 278?&lt;BR /&gt;If I want to overwrite the confirmed quantity with 278 through the available control check, it&amp;nbsp;does not take over 276, but only 500:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="AnkeWerner_1-1729599097981.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/182366i9C248373721D127A/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="AnkeWerner_1-1729599097981.png" alt="AnkeWerner_1-1729599097981.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Thank you in advance!&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/supply-chain-management-q-a/scheduling-agreement-confirmed-quantity-is-higher-than-open-quantity/qaq-p/13915666"/>
    <published>2024-10-22T14:31:30.620000+02:00</published>
